  "description": "The story's antagonist across both timelines. In 1985, he is George McFly's supervisor and still bullies him decades after high school. In 1955, he is the thuggish school bully who terrorises George and pursues Lorraine aggressively. His defeat at the dance — when George punches him unconscious — reshapes the power dynamic for the next thirty years.",
